  ('687a5f57-ed36-49e2-b94c-7053634c8336','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',74.0,'weak age proxy via 80yr tenure suggests owner 65+, +4 long-tenure 80yr',85.0,'multi-staff (35 emp) 80yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book; AS9100 +10 (aerospace premium), ISO 9001 +5',42.0,'1 coasting tell: same shop 1970s-90s (long-tenure tell)',78.0,'Metro=San Antonio; nudge +3 (aerospace/defense Kelly AFB). SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',68.0,'B_forward','Anthony Machine (San Antonio, TX) — 80yr CNC shop, owner ~?. L1=74 | L2=85 | L3=42 | L4=78 -> final=68 (B_forward). Certs: ISO 9001, AS9100. Coasting tells: 1 matched. Enrichment note: OUTSTANDING ETA PROFILE: 80-yr tenure (oldest in this batch), ISO 9001 + AS 9100 certified, multiple industry associations. Multi-generation Anthony family ownership likely (3rd or 4th gen). Inner-SA legacy real estate likely owned outright. Strong candidate for retirement-driven sale. SOS lookup priority.','operational tightening + ERP/quoting digitization to drive EBITDA uplift.','medium',0.7),
  ('858986cd-14cb-4cd4-a638-8ec3240dfea4','becddbcf-bcef-4bb1-80b9-95fed0635545',70.0,'owner ~60 (58-62 band), +4 long-tenure 30yr',75.0,'multi-staff (25 emp) 30yr tenure — solid SBA-financeable book; ISO 9001 +5',67.0,'2 coasting tells: social media absent; tell: family-owned',50.0,'Metro=Rural; nudge -3. SBA-financeable buyer access typical.',67.0,'B_forward','C & M Machining LP (Navasota, TX) — 30yr CNC shop, owner ~60. L1=70 | L2=75 | L3=67 | L4=50 -> final=67 (B_forward). Certs: ISO 9001. Coasting tells: 2 matched. Enrichment note: Family-owned 30yr rural Navasota shop, ISO 9001 + 34K sqft, MANUAL MILLS in equipment list = old-school posture. Owner partnership C + M (likely husband/wife or sibling). POTENTIAL A-TIER. Same legal entity as Sugar Land branch (deduplicate at finalization).','operational tightening + ERP/quoting digitization to drive EBITDA uplift.','medium',0.65),
